  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Enacts the \"low-carbon building construction act\"; relates to requiring construction of any building, addition or renovation greater than 25,000 square feet meet certain standards intended to reduce the embodied carbon emissions associated with the construction."
    }
